      "content": "i hear you, but honestly the diazepam alone is making me feel super heavy and out of it the next morning. i read somewhere that a little bit of alcohol might actually help level out the feeling so i don't feel so \"drugged\" and more just naturally sleepy. if i only have like a few sips, is there any real risk of it being life-threatening or are you just being extra cautious here?",
